@cityandguildsrecently held an Apprenticeship Nominee event to allow centres to congratulate their apprentices for their efforts during Covid-19.

Our apprentice's were nominated and received a great message from C&G.

For more information visit -https://buff.ly/30xkztc

@cityandguildsare supporting people looking for work in social care.

The Step into Social Care course explores whether a career in social care is right for you and learn about the skills you need to work as a career in the sector.

Apply herehttp://WeCare.wales/step-into-socinto-social-care-with-city-guilds/…
